cu.explanation_en: Setting the active gNB name to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the CU gNB from starting.

du.explanation_en: Setting the active gNB name to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure and prevent the DU gNB from starting.
du.explanation_zh: 將活躍 gNB 名稱設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致配置解析失敗，並阻止 DU gNB 啟動。
